---
const logos = [
  {
    name: "Colegio Los Robles",
    src: "/assets/img/marcas/colegio-los-robles-logo.png",
  },
  {
    name: "Colegio SM",
    src: "/assets/img/marcas/colegio-sm.png",
  },
  {
    name: "Colegio Nuevo",
    src: "/assets/img/marcas/cole-nuevo.png",
  },
  {
    name: "Municipalidad de Mercedes",
    src: "/assets/img/marcas/municipalidad-mercedes.png",
  },
  {
    name: "Medifé",
    src: "/assets/img/marcas/medife.png",
  },
  {
    name: "Swiss Medical",
    src: "/assets/img/marcas/swiss-medical-logo.png",
  },
  {
    name: "Axion Energy",
    src: "/assets/img/marcas/axion.png",
  },
  {
    name: "Shell Box",
    src: "/assets/img/marcas/shell-box.png",
  },
];
---

<section
  class="bg-[var(--color-bg)] text-[var(--color-text)] py-16 px-6 text-center animate-fade-in"
  role="region"
  aria-labelledby="brands-title"
>
  <h2 id="brands-title" class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold font-title mb-4">
    Confían en nosotros
  </h2>

  <p
    class="text-sm sm:text-base text-[var(--color-text)]/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed"
  >
    Empresas, colegios y organizaciones que han confiado en nosotros para
    desarrollar talleres y propuestas educativas.
  </p>

  <ul
    class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6
      place-items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto"
  >
    {
      logos.map((logo) => (
        <li
          class={`
            flex items-center justify-center p-4
            bg-[var(--glass-bg)] border border-[var(--glass-border)]
            rounded-xl shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.03] group
            w-full h-20
          `}
        >
          <img
            src={logo.src}
            alt={`Logo de ${logo.name}`}
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="
              max-h-12 object-contain
              opacity-90 group-hover:opacity-100
              sm:grayscale sm:group-hover:grayscale-0
              transition duration-300 ease-in-out
            "
          />
        </li>
      ))
    }
  </ul>
</section>
